    • Method Detail

      • createHull

        private void createHull(java.util.ArrayList<java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double> points)
        This method is the starting point of the QuickHull algorithm. In case the size of the ArrayList is to small to calculate a hull the is not much to do. Otherwise calling the getExtremalIndices(ArrayList) method calculates the left most and right most point. Both are added to the hull and two sets are created. Staying at point A and looking to point B one set represents all remaining points lying on the left and the other represents all lying on the right. With these two sets the calculateHullSet(Point2D.Double, Point2D.Double, ArrayList, ArrayList) method is called twice to recursively calculate the other points on the hull.
        Parameters:
        points - - an ArrayList of Point2D.Double.

      • getExtremalIndices

        private int[] getExtremalIndices(java.util.ArrayList<java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double> points)
        This method finds the index of the point of the ArrayList which is at most on the left and of the point which is at most on the right.
        Parameters:
        points - - a ArrayList of Point2D.Double.
        Returns:
        a Array of int values. The first represents the index of the left most point and the second the index of the rights most point.

      • calculateHullSet

        private void calculateHullSet(java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double a,
                    java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double b,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double> set,
                    java.util.ArrayList<java.awt.geom.Point2D.Double> hull)
        This method represents the divide step. A subset is processed. The furthest distance from A or B to a point P of the subset is found. P is added to the convexHull. Afterwards the subsets for the next step are builded an the recursive call is made.
        Parameters:
        a - - a Point2D.Double object.
        b - - a Point2D.Double object.
        set - - a ArrayList of Point2D.Double representing the processed subset.
        hull - - a ArrayList of Point2D.Double representing the hull so far.
